    <h1>About This Directory</h1>

    <p>
      Finding a mechanic you can trust shouldn't mean scrolling through Yelp reviews from people who've never been to Schuylkill County. We built this directory because Coal Region drivers deserve to find local, honest auto shops without the guesswork.
    </p>

    <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
    <p>
      When your check engine light comes on or you slide into a guardrail on a snowy Route 61 morning, you need a shop you can trust — fast. National platforms bury the best local shops behind paid ads and SEO games. The mechanic your neighbor's been going to for 20 years? Good luck finding him on page one of Google.
    </p>
    <p>
      This directory puts every auto repair shop, body shop, tire center, and towing service in Schuylkill County in one place. No paid rankings. No mystery algorithms. Just the shops that keep Coal Region cars on the road.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Include</h2>
    <p>
      Every listing includes publicly available information: name, address, phone number, website, and Google ratings where available. We don't accept payment for placement or rankings — listings are organized alphabetically by city.
    </p>

    <h2>About Antigravity</h2>
    <p>
      This directory is maintained by <strong>Antigravity Digital Services</strong>, helping local businesses in the Coal Region strengthen their online presence. We believe the shops keeping your car running deserve modern tools to reach the people who need them.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="/contact/">Have a question or correction? Contact us.</a>
    </p>
